{"tid":2176246,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"快艇和湖人支持球季直接結束，但多數的球隊仍希望把賽季打完","createTime":"2020-08-27T03:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T16:07:23.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"60676b794e42fcd41c402b7969f61020956188eb","tid":2176246,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"〔體育中心／綜合報導〕由於美國近日發生非裔男子遭警方槍擊事件，引發NBA球員怒火，今包含公鹿、湖人等球隊在內選擇罷賽。根據美國記者拉查尼亞（Shams Charania）消息，快艇和湖人已經投票抵制賽季，但多數球隊仍希望賽季進行，不過湖人一哥詹姆斯（LeBron James）則希望有更多老闆參與行動，會議中選擇直接離席。<br />\n<br />\n今日比賽確定取消後，目前球員和教練正在進行會議，商討接下來的應對辦法，與會的主要人員包含湖人一哥詹姆斯、球員工會主席保羅及快艇主帥瑞佛斯等人。根據美國記者拉查尼亞消息，會議中進行投票，快艇和湖人支持球季直接結束，但多數的球隊仍希望把賽季打完，且球員們也在會議中出現激烈言語交鋒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/breakingnews/3273006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3273006&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkxUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=1f605b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3273006&h=6d3ae80b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/breakingnews/3273006</a>"},{"pid":"c7c45fe19624deb416c34ded5176a407942ba64b","tid":2176246,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n占士勢力大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b784b6c7d0ad2dc1508a7b39fe949857cbb32552","tid":2176246,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"有人民幣賺就可以啦。"},{"pid":"b5a45ad686985cd03e18629fa2050bdf2a7bfbe5","tid":2176246,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"占士呢個決定分分鐘令佢歷史地位直接超越MJ<br />\n人權鬥士呢下超越哂籃球本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hk